Name: Average time from 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' to 'SW-Reviewer Declined'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Average time between 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' for cases where reviewers are reassigned
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time elapsed for all instances of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' within a manuscript's review cycle
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Reviewer Declined and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time observed from 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' to 'SW-Reviewer Declined'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'Assign a Different Editor' in cases where this action follows a decline
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'Assign a Different Editor'

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' until 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' is performed again
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average waiting time to 'SW-Reviewer Declined' after 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Total time it takes from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to the next 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' or 'SW-Reviewer Declined' event
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Reviewer Declined'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' or activity == 'SW-Reviewer Declined'", 'aggregation': 'total'}

Name: Minimum time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' reassignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time it takes from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 2' in cases where reminders are still sent
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 2'

Name: Total time for all 'SW-Reviewer Declined' activities within a single manuscript review process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Reviewer Declined and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' across all variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' before a manuscript is either accepted or receives a decision of major/minor revision
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Reviewer Declined'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Accept' or activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision'", 'aggregation': 'minimum'}

Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' in the review process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total time from the first 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to the final decision for a manuscript, whether accept, reject, or revision
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Reviewer Declined'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Accept' or activity == 'SW-EIC Reject' or activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision'", 'aggregation': 'total'}
